{"tid":2068858,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[活動改期］末日求生 超限戰爭集會 將改期到7月3日","createTime":"2020-06-18T03:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T11:01:10.000Z","uid":42194,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20f5d953575b611dad5a628561b7ee09e4b8ba6f","tid":2068858,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">末日求生 超限戰爭<br />\n抗爭週年集會<br />\n<br />\n活動改期</span><br />\n <br />\n日期 : 2020.7.3 (Fri)<br />\n時間 : 晚上7時至9時<br />\n地點 : 添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n*已通知警方，待發不反對通知書<br />\n**如限聚令再延長，將於限聚令結束後當日再聚<br />\n<br />\n#民間集會團隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WyjmE8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WyjmE8.jpg&h=c96bca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U7EZmFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU7EZmFe.jpg&h=af57e48d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要同各位手足講句唔好意思，因為集會要再度改期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對無理嘅政治打壓限聚令，如果我地唔改期，就只會換來一紙反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n民集一直以黎致力於舉辦讓在場不論和勇手足都可以安全參與的活動，而在反對通知書之下，我們既不可能宣傳活動，音響器材亦不可能進場，更重要的是我地連一點點確保手足安全的信心都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n故此，我地只好繼續改期，繼續追擊限聚令完結的第一天。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我地亦會發揮香港人嘅無限創意去進行抗爭，你有你打壓，我有我辦法，就好似之前612遍地開花社區展覽咁樣，我地成功令612記念活動遍地開花，融入社區。即使傳統集會被反對，民集依然會用各種不同方式，與香港人一同發聲。<br />\n<br />\n但係，傳統方式嘅集會去俾手足聚集，集氣，以人數表態，發聲，同樣重要。我地已經一切準備就緒，音響，嘉賓，run down, 內容，萬事俱備，只欠東風。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係民集同香港人嘅約定，只待時機來到，我哋就一定會集會再聚！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n民集堅信，香港人嘅耐力，勇氣，意志並唔會就此消磨。<br />\n<br />\n7月3日，城下再聚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊<br />\n2020年6月18日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s. 6月29日係盧曉欣手足死忌，請大家記念，並繼承她的意志。"},{"pid":"5ff8814d03a2af5cef1f5489614f4fc74e415858","tid":2068858,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:51:46.000Z","msg":"｛集氣｝7月4日美國獨立日，美國領事館大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2064169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2064169</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c78472de32963356463172eb77bedba775ed2848","tid":2068858,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:52:28.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bfcc416b6710d94a41ebed82b586fcb45b7b1c1e","tid":2068858,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:52:42.000Z","msg":"永續限聚令 咁姐係唔駛再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa5d79623b47add2d685f2973d282749157c7f8","tid":2068858,"uid":293543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"不如搞個遊行關於法院，向國際說明香港法治已死"},{"pid":"c3e9bb58b4c731188df6524ad67962c2edd08fd5","tid":2068858,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21524d12564869ab0bb785dfab3cf912af7d2f3a","tid":2068858,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728ddea6408ac9b1cb693dea0b8f3c6d55f38993","tid":2068858,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5768ed4657fbdf2ec73d1d00492de3818bbfb8ad","tid":2068858,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"限聚令好撚煩"}]}